[Enter feedback here]
Under Windows 10 mitigations that you can configure, for Microsoft Defender Antivirus the description is awkward.

The sentence "Microsoft Defender Antivirus has been improved to a considerable extent since it was introduced...."

It may be better "Microsoft Defender Antivirus has improved considerably since it was introduced...."

